title: Narrative

* This example shows ''tagField'' across multiple toc macro variants

* Uses a `tag-like` field instead of standard tags to build the tree

* Compares toc-selective-expandable, with and without `exclude`, and simple toc

* The `exclude` parameter removes `todo1` and `todo2`, so `bb` should not show a chevron

+
title: Description

tagField with selective-expandable, exclude, and simple toc
+
title: tag-like-root

Root node for tag-like hierarchy

+
title: aaa
tag-like: tag-like-root

+
title: aaa.a
tag-like: aaa

+
title: aaa.b
tag-like: aaa

+
title: aaa.b.1
tag-like: aaa.b

+
title: bb
caption: bb-caption
tag-like: tag-like-root
toc-include: [tag[todo]]

bb has toc-include for todo items

+
title: todo1
tags: todo
toc-link: no

+
title: todo2
tags: todo

+
title: ccc
tag-like: tag-like-root

+
title: tag-like-c
tag-like: ccc

+
title: tag-like-d
tag-like: ccc

